snippet.title: Top best performances of Elliot Page
snippet.description:
Top best performances of Elliot Page
Recently, Hollywood star Ellen Page has officially declared herself transgender and changed her name to Elliot Page. The actor born in 1987 is one of Hollywood's leading faces when he is appreciated for his roles in major blockbusters with excellent acting skill.  In today video, we’ll pick up some of his best performances. Let's enjoy.

#ElliotPage
